# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NAFIJPRO-DOWNLOADER (DownAria) — Deployment Guide
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Architecture:
#   Frontend (fauntend/) → Vercel    → nafijthepro-downloader.vercel.app
#                                    → downloader.nafij.me  (custom domain)
#                                    → downloader.nafijrahaman.me (custom domain)
#   Backend  (backend/)  → Render    → nafijthepro-downloader.onrender.com
#
# Auto-connect flow:
#   Browser → Vercel (Next.js rewrites) ──JSON──▶ Render :10000
#   Browser ────────────────────────────streaming▶ Render :10000 (direct)
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  cp backend/.env.example  backend/.env
#  cp fauntend/.env.example fauntend/.env.local
#
#  npm install              # root — installs concurrently
#  npm run install:frontend # frontend deps
#  npm run dev              # starts backend :8081 + frontend :3001
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RENDER DEPLOYMENT  (Backend — Go + Docker)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  URL: https://nafijthepro-downloader.onrender.com
#
#  1. New Web Service → connect GitHub repo
#  2. Settings:
#       Root Directory : backend
#       Runtime        : Docker
#       Dockerfile Path: ./Dockerfile
#  3. Environment Variables in Render Dashboard:
#
#     PORT=10000
#     ENV=production
#     WEB_INTERNAL_SHARED_SECRET=<strong-random-secret>
#     ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://nafijthepro-downloader.vercel.app,https://downloader.nafij.me,https://downloader.nafijrahaman.me
#     MERGE_ENABLED=true
#     UPSTREAM_TIMEOUT_MS=15000
#     MAX_DOWNLOAD_SIZE_MB=512
#     CACHE_EXTRACTION_TTL=5m
#     GLOBAL_RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW=60/1m
#
#  NOTE: render.yaml at repo root handles this automatically
#        if you use the Render Blueprint deploy button.
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VERCEL DEPLOYMENT  (Frontend — Next.js)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  URL    : https://nafijthepro-downloader.vercel.app
#  Custom : https://downloader.nafij.me
#  Custom : https://downloader.nafijrahaman.me
#
#  1. Import project → vercel.com → "Add New Project"
#  2. Root Directory: fauntend
#  3. Framework: Next.js (auto-detected)
#  4. Environment Variables in Vercel Dashboard:
#
#     NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=https://downloader.nafij.me
#     NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://nafijthepro-downloader.onrender.com
#     BACKEND_URL=https://nafijthepro-downloader.onrender.com
#     NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=<supabase-project-url>
#     NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<supabase-anon-key>
#
#  5. Custom Domains → Settings → Domains:
#       downloader.nafij.me        → CNAME → cname.vercel-dns.com
#       downloader.nafijrahaman.me → CNAME → cname.vercel-dns.com
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
